From: Lei Huang <huanglei@kylinos.cn>
Date: Tue, 31 Mar 2026 15:54:05 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] ALSA: hda/realtek: fix code style (ERROR: else should follow close brace '}')
Git-commit: d1888bf848ade6a9e71c7ba516fd215aa1bd8d65
Patch-mainline: v7.1-rc1
References: git-fixes

Fix checkpatch code style errors:

  ERROR: else should follow close brace '}'
  #2300: FILE: sound/pci/hda/patch_realtek.c:2300:
  +       }
  +       else

Fixes: 31278997add6 ("ALSA: hda/realtek - Add headset quirk for Dell DT")
Signed-off-by: Lei Huang <huanglei@kylinos.cn>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20260331075405.78148-1-huanglei814@163.com
Signed-off-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
 sound/pci/hda/patch_realtek.c |    4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

--- a/sound/pci/hda/patch_realtek.c
+++ b/sound/pci/hda/patch_realtek.c
@@ -6178,9 +6178,9 @@ static void alc_fixup_headset_mode_alc25
 		struct alc_spec *spec = codec->spec;
 		spec->parse_flags |= HDA_PINCFG_HEADSET_MIC;
 		alc255_set_default_jack_type(codec);
-	}
-	else
+	} else {
 		alc_fixup_headset_mode(codec, fix, action);
+	}
 }
 
 static void alc288_update_headset_jack_cb(struct hda_codec *codec,
